# Contributing to [Project Name]

Thank you for considering contributing to this project! Here are some guidelines to help you get started.

## Submitting Issues
1. Check the [issues page](https://github.com/your-repository-name/issues) to ensure the issue doesn't already exist.
2. If your issue isn't listed, click **"New Issue"** and provide a clear and concise description.
3. Include steps to reproduce the issue, screenshots, and any relevant information.

## Creating Pull Requests
1. Fork the repository and clone your fork locally.
2. Create a new branch for your feature or bugfix:
   ```bash
   git checkout -b feature-or-bug-name
